type	 冒险, 独立, 角色扮演				
desc_short	-----								Why Am I Dead At Sea is an adventure game where you solve the mystery of your own murder. As a ghost, you will have to possess people and use them to investigate your surroundings. But in this place no one is who they seem...and everyone has a secret.							
developer									Peltast Software								
